metadata.name: Alone Woman
metadata.description:
Darkness has a majesty that drives people crazy.
The stars are in clusters in the air like bright ideas.
I'm alone as a mountain top tonight.
Flowers are dripping from the fingers of the night.
An old school song on my lips.
My hands stretched out towards you in the dark.
My eyes are constantly searching for your eyes.
Where are you?
